Package pt.uc.dei.dtos

Class UserDTO

java.lang.Object
pt.uc.dei.dtos.UserDTO
Direct Known Subclasses:
UserFullDTO, UserResponseDTO
public class UserDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a user. Stores user details including authentication credentials, personal information, and role data.
